==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nonintervention
<hw>Non*in`ter*ven"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state
or habit of not intervening or interfering; <as>as, the
<ex>nonintervention</ex> of one state in the affairs of
another</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>non-involvement</ent>⟦br⟧
